  - m_Id: 376430611
    m_Localized: Timed Exit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430612
    m_Localized: This block must reach the exit within a limited number of moves.
      The counter decreases after every move. If the counter reaches zero before
      the block exits, the level fails.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430613
    m_Localized: Locked Until Clears
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430614
    m_Localized: This block cannot move at the beginning. A required number of other
      blocks must exit first. Once the condition is completed, the block becomes
      active.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430615
    m_Localized: Horizontal Move
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430616
    m_Localized: This block can only move left and right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430617
    m_Localized: Vertical Move
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430618
    m_Localized: This block can only move up and down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430619
    m_Localized: Nested Shape
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 376430620
    m_Localized: This block contains nested layers. When the outer layer exits,
      the next inner layer appears and continues from the same position.
